OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1772129063
OL,3,CBurst water pipe causes huge flooding
OL,4,Cin Islington
OL,6,FA huge flood has taken hold in
OL,7,FIslington after a burst water pipe.
OL,9,FTorrents of water could be seen
OL,10,Fcovering large areas of the Caledonian
OL,11,FRoad, with levels in some places
OL,12,Freaching halfway up the wheels of a
OL,13,Fcar.
OL,15,FThames Water said customers at N1, N7,
OL,16,FWC1X and EC1R postcodes may be
OL,17,Fexperiencing low water pressure or no
OL,18,Fwater.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/2
