OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1772129063
OL,3,CBurst water pipe causes huge flooding
OL,4,Cin Islington
OL,6,FIt said: "We apologise to those who
OL,7,Fare currently being affected by a
OL,8,Fburst water main on Caledonian Road,
OL,9,FN1.
OL,11,F"Our teams are on the way to stop the
OL,12,Fflow of water and then carry out the
OL,13,Frepair as quickly and safely as they
OL,14,Fcan."
OL,16,FMore updates to follow
